desc: Ebu's Enchanted Gift Shop is filled with one of a kind pieces made by local artisans as well as artists from around the world. You will also find illuminating candles, sage flower bundles, fairies & elves, beautifully blended sachets, wool birdhouses, fairy dwellings and other wondrous treasures! ​

layout.text: Add a Little Whimsy with Unique Handcrafted
